title: Sorry bout 420
author: TheRealDragoonie
pages:
#- Today I was bored and went to vale, city of the collaborators. Jezzaindahouse was making some sort of valeian collaboration divice he would not show me or tell me how it worked. Then lil_wayne69420 (Jakemeister's alt) came up and robbed me for my Sharp 4 
#- Knockback 2 Fireaspect 2 Unbreaking 3 sword. He asked "Whai de sharp 4 on sword?" I replied, "cuz i got more swag then lil wayne." jakemeister was not very pleased that I said that so he challenged me to a pokemon battle.
#- I got mad because lil_wayne69420 always beats me in pvp cuz he say he got more swag and 420 than me. So I hit him in the face with my Steak and he said I gotta write a book and I'm very Snoori about it :(.
